/2016-07-21/59755219.html|archive-date=2018-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=人间正道：审判红色高棉|url=http://news.ifeng.com/history/special/khmerrouge/|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[凤凰网|凤凰网]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305135040/http://news.ifeng.com/history/special/khmerrouge/|archive-date=2009-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=中国何时坦然面对自身历史污点？|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20150331/c31history/|author=Dan Levin|date=2015-03-31|last=|first=|format=|work=|publisher=《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007214719/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20150331/c31history/|archive-date=2019-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=金边的毛泽东大道|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/blvd-mao-tse-toung-in-phnom-penh-20191001/5104674.html|author=莉雅|date=2019-10-03|coauthors=海伦|work=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003233301/https://www.voachinese.com/a/blvd-mao-tse-toung-in-phnom-penh-20191001/5104674.html|archive-date=2019-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据学者统计，中国的援助占红色高棉总外援的至少90%，仅在1975年，中方就向红色高棉提供了至少10亿[[美元|美元]]的无息经济和军事援助以及2000万美元的“礼物”<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":24">{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Mq8sAcvg-AgC&printsec=frontcover&dq=ben+kiernan+pol+pot+regime+$1+billion+China+1975&hl=en&newbks=1&newbks_redir=0&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj8s42l84jmAhX1GjQIHf_8BQAQ6AEwAHoECAMQAg#v=onepage&q=ben%20kiernan%20pol%20pot%20regime%20$1%20billion%20China%201975&f=false|publisher=Yale University Press|date=2008-10|isbn=978-0-300-14299-0|language=en|first=Ben|last=Kiernan|title=The Pol Pot Regime: Race, Power, and Genocide in Cambodia Under the Khmer Rouge, 1975-79|year=|location=|pages=|access-date=2019-11-27|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703055536/https://books.google.com/books?id=Mq8sAcvg-AgC&printsec=frontcover&dq=ben+kiernan+pol+pot+regime+%241+billion+China+1975&hl=en&newbks=1&newbks_redir=0&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj8s42l84jmAhX1GjQIHf_8BQAQ6AEwAHoECAMQAg#v=onepage&q=ben%20kiernan%20pol%20pot%20regime%20$1%20billion%20China%201975&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":25">{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=54iUDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA84&lpg=PA84&dq=By+mid-september+China+was+prepared+to+extend+to+Cambodia+a+total+of+US$1+billion&source=bl&ots=TR7nx5RuUi&sig=ACfU3U3UtmdKsrzOo5JRZ2KslPKlSWTzVQ&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj5wqfQ8YjmAhX5IDQIHTAIAUgQ6AEwAHoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=By%20mid-september%20China%20was%20prepared%20to%20extend%20to%20Cambodia%20a%20total%20of%20US$1%20billion&f=false|publisher=Policy Press|date=2019-05-08|isbn=978-1-5292-0221-2|language=en|first=Southgate|last=Laura|title=ASEAN Resistance to Sovereignty Violation: Interests, Balancing and the Role of the Vanguard State|year=|location=|pages=|access-date=2019-11-27|archive-date=2021-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703055628/https://books.google.com/books?id=54iUDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA84&lpg=PA84&dq=By+mid-september+China+was+prepared+to+extend+to+Cambodia+a+total+of+US%241+billion&source=bl&ots=TR7nx5RuUi&sig=ACfU3U3UtmdKsrzOo5JRZ2KslPKlSWTzVQ&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj5wqfQ8YjmAhX5IDQIHTAIAUgQ6AEwAHoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=By%20mid-september%20China%20was%20prepared%20to%20extend%20to%20Cambodia%20a%20total%20of%20US$1%20billion&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":11">{{Cite web|title=2016:张春桥幽灵|url=http://ywang.uchicago.edu/history/docs/2016_12_30.pdf|accessdate=|author=王友琴|date=2016年|authorlink=王友琴|format=|publisher=[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703025123/http://ywang.uchicago.edu/history/docs/2016_12_30.pdf|archive-date=2021-07-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":16">{{Cite web|title=“十月革命”一百周年专访王友琴之二：以鸟和虫的眼睛记录历史（ RFA张敏）|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/zhuanlan/xinlingzhilyu/lishihuiyinbi/mind-11222017133719.html|author=|date=2017-11-22|format=|work=|publisher=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117003103/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/zhuanlan/xinlingzhilyu/lishihuiyinbi/mind-11222017133719.html|archive-date=2019-11-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1975年4月，红色高棉在柬埔寨取得实权后，开始激进推行[[共产主义|共产主义]]，期间中共中央主席毛泽东亲自接见了[[波尔布特|波尔布特]]，而[[中国共产党中央政治局常务委员会|中共中央政治局常委]][[张春桥|张春桥]]等人还亲自访问柬埔寨进行了“指导”并表示肯定<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":9" /><ref name=":13">{{Cite web|title=红色高棉运动始末|url=https://boxun.com/news/gb/z_special/2016/01/201601132346.shtml|author=于洪君|date=2016-01-13|format=|work=[[博讯|博讯]]|publisher=[[共识网|共识网]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203060421/http://boxun.com/news/gb/z_special/2016/01/201601132346.shtml|archive-date=2018-02-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。红色高棉试图创建一个[[农业社会主义|农业社会主义]]的社会，故强迫城市人口全部迁移到乡下，并效仿中国实行“[[大跃进|大跃进]]（Maha lout ploh）”，导致大量人死于疾病、过度劳动或营养不良<ref name=":31" /><ref name="Chandler256">钱德勒，256页</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mTlMDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT77&lpg=PT77&dq=Maha+lout+ploh&source=bl&ots=6FCzmoGoUn&sig=ACfU3U1z6BjPUp21ju-IPyATlDmoRadWXg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj92dnZqYHmAhVXvZ4KHTAeBeoQ6AEwAHoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=Maha%20lout%20ploh&f=false|publisher=Routledge|date=2018-02-02|isbn=978-0-429-98161-6|language=en|first=David P.|last=Chandler|title=Brother Number One: A Political Biography Of Pol Pot|year=|location=|pages=|access-date=2019-11-24|archive-date=2021-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606114628/https://books.google.com/books?id=mTlMDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT77&lpg=PT77&dq=Maha+lout+ploh&source=bl&ots=6FCzmoGoUn&sig=ACfU3U1z6BjPUp21ju-IPyATlDmoRadWXg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj92dnZqYHmAhVXvZ4KHTAeBeoQ6AEwAHoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=Maha%20lout%20ploh&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xZSpDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA334&lpg=PA334&dq=Maha+lout+ploh&source=bl&ots=0SyoIw3VU_&sig=ACfU3U3OrjDUNgI-xBLsqiI4oIBzSTxn8g&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj92dnZqYHmAhVXvZ4KHTAeBeoQ6AEwAXoECAoQAQ#v=onepage&q=Maha%20lout%20ploh&f=false|publisher=Routledge|date=2018-05-04|isbn=978-0-429-96406-0|language=en|first=David|last=Chandler|title=A History of Cambodia|year=|location=|pages=|access-date=2019-11-24|archive-date=2021-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606114642/https://books.google.com/books?id=xZSpDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA334&lpg=PA334&dq=Maha+lout+ploh&source=bl&ots=0SyoIw3VU_&sig=ACfU3U3OrjDUNgI-xBLsqiI4oIBzSTxn8g&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj92dnZqYHmAhVXvZ4KHTAeBeoQ6AEwAXoECAoQAQ#v=onepage&q=Maha%20lout%20ploh&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时，波尔布特等人宣称要“洗净平民”，因而开始杀戮<ref name=":0" />{{sfn|Hannum|1989|pp=88-89}}；自1976年起，波尔布特又认为“党的躯体已经生病了”，于是开始了对柬埔寨共产党内部人员的大清洗，中央高层领导以及军队总参谋部几乎被屠杀殆尽，1978年仅在柬埔寨东部地区就有十万干部和军人被杀<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=《1984》现实版：红色高棉统治下的人间炼狱|url=https://www.chinesepen.org/blog/archives/131772|author=柬易|date=2019-06-27|format=|work=[[独立中文笔会|独立中文笔会]]|publisher=|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810032458/https://www.chinesepen.org/blog/archives/131772|archive-date=2019-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=红色高棉:空前绝后的恐怖执政|url=http://www.people.com.cn/GB/198221/198819/198849/12413473.html|author=燕妮|date=2010-08-11|format=|work=[[人民网|人民网]]|publisher=《文史参考》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824165247/http://www.people.com.cn/GB/198221/198819/198849/12413473.html|archive-date=2018-08-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=红色高棉大事记|url=http://www1.rfi.fr/actucn/articles/111/article_12608.asp|author=凯文|date=2009-03-13|format=|work=|publisher=[[法国国际广播电台|法国国际广播电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606141015/http://www1.rfi.fr/actucn/articles/111/article_12608.asp|archive-date=2021-06-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[法国|法国]]学者[[让·拉库尔特|让·拉库尔特]]發明“[[自我屠殺|自我屠殺]]”一词来形容红色高棉<ref name=":33">{{Cite web|title=以革命的名义：红色高棉大屠杀揭秘|url=https://news.ifeng.com/history/1/midang/200803/0304_2664_423347.shtml|date=2008-03-04|work=[[凤凰网|凤凰网]]|publisher=千龙网|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220117042252/https://news.ifeng.com/history/1/midang/200803/